chart.name: Service map
chart.programText: B = data('spans.count', filter=filter('kind', 'CONSUMER', 'SERVER') and filter('service', '*') and filter('cluster', '*')).sum(by=['service']).publish(label='B')

chart.description: Error rate on requests made to the service
chart.name: Error rate
chart.programText:
A = data('spans.count', filter=filter('kind', 'SERVER', 'CONSUMER') and filter('error', 'false') and filter('service', '*') and filter('cluster', '*'), rollup='delta').sum(by=['service']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('spans.count', filter=filter('kind', 'SERVER', 'CONSUMER') and filter('service', '*') and filter('cluster', '*'), rollup='delta').sum(by=['service']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (100*(B-A)/B).publish(label='C')

chart.description: Saturation of the service hosts (max of CPU, memory and disk utilization)
chart.name: Service hosts saturation
chart.programText:
A = data('cpu.utilization', filter=filter('sf_hasService', '*')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('memory.utilization', filter=filter('sf_hasService', '*')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = data('disk.summary_utilization', filter=filter('sf_hasService', '*')).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = max(A, B, C).sum(by='host').publish(label='D')
